title: Lynda - Building a Polling App with Socket IO and React.js
description:
Lynda - Building a Polling App with Socket IO and React.js

Uploaded in Sept 16, 2015 by 2boweb

Socket technology is a natural fit for presentation and chat applications. This course helps you use Socket IO in combination with powerful JavaScript libraries to develop an interactive polling application that processes data in real time, allowing presenters to interact with audience members and graph their responses
